## Deployment Summary

After each successful run, GitHub Actions posts a summary:

```
‚úÖ Deployment Complete
- Run:      #6
- Commit:   19a86ddcdd4e733efdee75eea63decf827f67f76
- Image:    myregistry.azurecr.io/azurepoc:19a86dd...
- Revision: v6-19a86dd

Active Revisions
Revision                   Traffic  Created
poc-app-dev--v6-19a86dd    100      2026-03-18T17:30:00
poc-app-dev--v5-f0af0d1    0        2026-03-18T15:00:00
```